### Description:

This avoids typescript errors when casting certain arbitrary objects to the QueryParameters type. I was specifically having trouble with this one:

```
{
 example: string;
 name: string;
 types: {
 name: string;
 value: string;
 }[];
 value: string;
}[]
```

